BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Library of Congress] 2026 Innovator in Residence Informational We
 binar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260314
DTSTAMP:20260314T224131Z
UID:da0918d1-cdb8-4bd9-b51e-e4de8d59cc1a@dc-events-calendar
CATEGORIES:Cultural Centers,Library of Congress
DESCRIPTION:The Library of Congress is seeking its next Innovator in Resid
 ence! Launched in 2017\, the program invites creative thinkers to connect 
